---
title: Hot to Trot Tortelloni Marinara with Peas & Herby Ricotta
description: Tender tortelloni stuffed with lots of cheese are great in any form, but add garlicky Tuscan-style marinara sauce, sweet peas, a drizzle of olive oil, and a dollop of herby ricotta on top, and you’ve got yourself an easy, massively tasty pasta lunch to remember. Did we mention that this recipe takes a quick 15 minutes to make? Be still, our pasta-loving hearts…
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65131e98b6b74f3addadb4d7-11e335c7.jpeg
